- 100% Skillcape Emotes - Working Webclient - Duel Arena - Runescape Style Website - More Too Come-

- 100% Chaos Prayers (Turmoil, Soulsplit, Delfect Meele and Sap Spirit) - Brand New PKing Minigame(Death Trap) - 100% Working Barrows with Kill Count, Crypts, and Chest. - Working Set Effect(All barrows, Void Etc.) - 24 7 Hosted - Amazing New SMF Forums! [Just Achived] - More To Come! -
